html
	head
		title= "The Hunt"
		script(src="/javascripts/countdown.js")
		script(src="/javascripts/global.js")
		link(rel="icon", href="/images/logo.png")
		script(src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js"   integrity="sha256-Qw82+bXyGq6MydymqBxNPYTaUXXq7c8v3CwiYwLLNXU="   crossorigin="anonymous")
		link(rel='stylesheet',href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css")
		script(src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js")
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/style.css')
	body
		nav(class="navbar navbar-static-top container-fluid",role="navigation",id="titlebar")
			div(class="navbar-inner container-fluid")
				div(class="navbar-header") 
					a(class="navbar-brand headertext", id="headertext") The Hunt
				ul(class="nav navbar-nav pull-right")
					li(class="active")
						a(href="#",id="navlink") FAQ
					li(class="active")
						a(href="#",id="navlink") Sponsorship/Media
					li(class="active")
						a(href="#",id="navlink") Contact Us
		div(class="jumbotron container-fluid row secondjumbo", id="bigfrontpageimage")
			div(id="explanatorytext")
				h1(class="frontheading",id="frontheading") Super fun paid scavenger hunt 
				b(id="smallheadingtext") The Hunt is an exhilarating, paid scavenger hunt that pits participants from the same city against each other in a battle of wits. Each participant pays $2, and the winner of the Hunt gets $100 or 25% of the money paid in. When you sign up, you receive a clue via email on a certain date. You (and your friends!) will decipher that clue, which will lead you to the next clue, and then the next clue, all taking place under two hours. The Hunt happens every few months. 
				br
				br
				b(id="smallheadingtext") The next hunt is on 
				b(id="smallheadingtext",class="datetext") #{date}. 
		div(class="jumbotron container-fluid row", id="frontpagejumbotron")
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
					div(class="row")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							img(src="/images/clue.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							i(id="jumbotext") Sign up for the Hunt in your city by entering an email below
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
						div(class="row")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							img(src="/images/treasure.jpg",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							i(id="jumbotext") Pay $2 and watch the money in the pot go up
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
					div(class="row")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							img(src="/images/key.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							i(id="jumbotext") Receive a clue via text on Hunt Day (#{date})
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
					div(class="row")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							img(src="/images/treasure.jpg",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						div(class="col-sm-6 text-center",style="height: 100%;")
							i(id="jumbotext") Follow the clues around Boston, until someone finds the final clue 
		div(class="container-fluid text-center pagination-centered nomarginrow" id="content")
				div(id="countdownholder" class="row")
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") Time until the next hunt on July 15th:
						div(id="countdown", class="lead")
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") Number of hunters signed up
						div(id="numberhunters",class="lead")
							p 52
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") Current prize amount
						div(id="prizeamount", class="lead")
							p $100
		div(id="hunt-join")
			form(id="form",action="/hunterjoin",method="post",onsubmit="return formvalidation()")
				input(type="text",id="HunterEmail",name="HunterEmail",style="color:#888;", value="Enter your email", onfocus="inputFocus(this)",onblur="inputBlur(this)")
				p(id="errormessageholder")
				div(id="submitbuttonholder")
					button(type="submit",action="post",id="frontpagesubmitbutton",class="submitbutton") I want to participate
			
					